org.mobicents.slee.runtime.sbbentity
Class SbbEntityFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.mobicents.slee.container.AbstractSleeContainerModule
      org.mobicents.slee.runtime.sbbentity.SbbEntityFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SbbEntityFactory, SleeContainerModule
public class SbbEntityFactoryImpl
extends AbstractSleeContainerModule
implements SbbEntityFactory

SbbEntityFactory -- implements a map from SBB Entity Id to SBB Entity instances. This is the sole place where Sbb Entities are created and destroyed. We keep a map of SBB Entity ID to SBB Entity here and return Sbb Entities that are stored in this map.

Author:
F.Moggia, M. Ranganathan, Tim Fox ( streamlining ), eduardomartins
